name: SentiSight
title: SentiSight

api_list.name: /image/{projectId}/{imageName}
/images/{projectId}
api_list.description: Get a list of image names

api_list.name: /similarity
api_list.description: Use NvN image similarity search. Returns a JSON array of similarity search results.

optional_parameters.name: threshold
optional_parameters.description: Only shows results above this threshold (value in percent)

optional_parameters.name: limit
optional_parameters.description: Limits the result count to this number

optional_parameters.name: and
optional_parameters.description: Use "and" operator instead of "or" for filtering images by labels

optional_parameters.name: labels
optional_parameters.description: Specify one or more image labels to filter the images in your data set prior to image similarity search, hence, reducing the search space. Can be empty.

api_list.name: /label/{projectId}/image/{imageName}
/label/{projectId}
